filter
I can apply the following filters: number of bedrooms, price, floor, balcony, elevator and nearby POIs.

Okay. Take notes. High floor at least 12. Balcony is a must. Elevator is a must. At least 2 bedrooms, more is okay. As for price, I don't want to live near poors any more. Only show me places that cost at least 1500.
one on center

OK, I found a free flat in One on Center Apartments, located near a School and a Park, that is matching your search criteria.
It is on level 12, has 86 square meters and 2 bedrooms.
It has a north facing balcony and has an elevator, and comes at the price of 1459 per month.
I was hoping to pay a little more than that. Is there anything a bit more expensive?
error

No, just schedule an appointment to look at that last one. I can use the leftover money to buy myself a ferrari.

Then, yes book the appointment, but not for 5 pm. Anytime before 3 is okay with me.
